\par }\pard \s16\qj \fi480\li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid3304115 {\insrsid3304115 \'93You see, Watson,\'94 he explained in the early hours of the morning as we sat over a glass of whisky and soda in Baker Street, 
