, must be to get this not over-bright pawnbroker out of the way for a number of hours every day. It was a curious way of managing it, but, really, it would be difficult to suggest a better. The method was no doubt suggested to Clay\rquote 
s ingenious mind by the colour of his accomplice\rquote s hair. The }{\i\insrsid3304115 \'a3}{\insrsid3304115 4 a week was a lure which must draw him, and what was it to them, who were playing for thousands? They put in the advertisement, one rogue has 
