ctoria.\'94 
\par \'93Ha! In Victoria! That is important.\'94 
\par \'93Yes, at the mines.\'94 
\par \'93Quite so; at the gold-mines, where, as I understand, Mr. Turner made his money.\'94 
\par \'93Yes, certainly.\'94 
\par \'93Thank you, Miss Turner. You have been of material assistance to me.\'94 
